Wɔn a wɔkabom hyehyɛɛ amanyɔkuo no ne kane amanyɔkuo Convention People’s Party mu fo a w’ate wɔn ho, kane amanyɔkuo United Gold Coast Conventions (UGCC) mu fo a w’ate wɔn ho ne amanyɔkuo a ɛne National Democratic Party a edii nkuguo pɔtɔɔ wɔ afe 1951 abatoɔ no mu, na egui no.

doc.title: Wikipedia: Emmanuel Obetsebi-Lamptey

Ɔka won a wɔhyehyɛɛ ɔman Ghana na afei nso ɔyɛ amanyɔkuo United Gold Coast Convention (UGCC) ahyehyɛfo ne akandifo a w’ato wɔn din ;’’The Big Six” no mu baako.
